<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us - Bharat Pashudhan</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    body, html {
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f7f9fd; /* Off-white background */
    }
    .main-content {
      flex: 1;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .about-container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 700px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.10);
      padding: 35px 30px;
      color: #003057;
      border: 1px solid #e3e8ee;
      z-index: 1;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .about-title {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      color: #003057;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .about-content {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #2d3a4a;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      text-align: justify;
    }
    .about-info {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .about-info i {
      color: #10b981;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }
    /* Contact Form Section */
    .contact-container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.10);
      padding: 35px 30px;
      color: #003057;
      border: 1px solid #e3e8ee;
      z-index: 1;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .contact-title {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      color: #003057;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .contact-info {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .contact-info i {
      color: #10b981;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }
    .contact-form label {
      font-weight: 600;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #003057;
    }
    .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 15px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      color: #003057;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
    }
    .contact-form input:focus, .contact-form textarea:focus {
      outline: none;
      border: 2px solid #3b82f6;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,1);
    }
    .contact-form textarea {
      resize: none;
      height: 80px;
    }
    .contact-form button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 0;
      background: #10b981;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .contact-form button:hover {
      background: #059669;
      color: #fff;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .contact-success {
      display: none;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      background: rgba(16,185,129,0.18);
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      color: #003057;
      animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease;
    }
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .main-content {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .about-container, .contact-container {
        padding: 18px 8px;
      }
      .about-title, .contact-title {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
      }
    }
    /* Header and Footer Fixes */
    header {
      background: #f7f9fd !important;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e3e8ee !important;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(31,38,135,0.04);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
    }
    header .left-section img,
    header .left-section .text,
    header .left-section div {
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    header nav a {
      color: #003057 !important;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding-bottom: 2px;
    }
    header nav a.active {
      border-bottom: 2px solid #0077b6;
    }
    .footer-container {
      background: #0a4d63 !important;
      color: white !important;
      border-top: 1px solid #e3e8ee;
      padding: 20px 40px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .footer-left img {
      height: 80px !important;
      clip-path: circle(40% at 50% 50%);
    }
    .footer-center, .footer-right {
      text-align: center;
      flex: 1;
    }
    .footer-center h3, .footer-right h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .footer-center p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .social-icons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .social-icons img {
      height: 25px;
      width: 25px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .version-info {
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: #d9e6f2;
    }
    footer {
      background: #0a4d63 !important;
      color: white !important;
      border-top: 1px solid #e3e8ee;
      box-shadow: 0 -2px 8px rgba(31,38,135,0.04);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  <div class="main-content">
    <div class="about-container">
      <div class="about-title">
        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> About Bharat Pashudhan
      </div>
      <div class="about-content">
        Bharat Pashudhan is an initiative by the Department of Animal Husbandry and Dairying, Government of India, in collaboration with NDDB. Our mission is to empower livestock owners and field workers with digital tools for animal registration, breed identification, and health management.<br><br>
        We strive to bring transparency, efficiency, and innovation to the livestock sector, ensuring better productivity and welfare for animals and their owners. Our platform leverages modern technology to simplify processes and provide valuable insights for all stakeholders.
      </div>
      <div class="about-info">
        <div>
          <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
          NDDB, Anand, Gujarat, India
        </div>
        <div>
          <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
          project.office@ndlm.co.in
        </div>
        <div>
          <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
          +91-12345-67890
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-container">
      <div class="contact-title">
        <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Contact Us
      </div>
      <form class="contact-form" id="contactForm">
        <label for="name">Your Name</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Enter your name" required>
        <label for="email">Your Email</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
        <label for="message">Message</label>
        <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Type your message" required></textarea>
        <button type="submit"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i> Send Message</button>
      </form>
      <div class="contact-success" id="contactSuccess">
        <i class="fas fa-check-circle success-icon"></i>
        <h3>Thank you!</h3>
        <p>Your message has been sent successfully.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      const contactForm = document.getElementById('contactForm');
      const contactSuccess = document.getElementById('contactSuccess');
      contactForm.addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        contactForm.style.display = 'none';
        contactSuccess.style.display = 'block';
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>